        "151": {
          "vnum": 151,
          "name": "Thal'adriel's Forge",
          "description": "The dugout stone structure rings with the steady clinking of hammer on anvil, and the air inside is several degrees warmer than the air outside. The interior is a mixture of new and old: original stonework still in place along two walls, freshly hewn timbers framing the rest. Weapon racks and armor stands line the walls. A sturdy anvil sits at the center.",
