          "npcs": [
            {
              "name": "King Eldraen",
              "description": "sharp without being thin, and his hair, dark when he was younger, has gone the color of pale steel at the temples.  He sits the throne the way a man sits a horse he has ridden for years - without effort, without gripping. His eyes are green, and they have not stopped tracking you since you entered",
              "unique": true
            },
            {
              "name": "Queen Tysara",
              "description": "twenty from across a room and ageless from a foot away.  Her eyes are a dark blue that is almost black except in candlelight.  She does not look as though she is doing anything in particular - only sitting, attentive - and yet you find that you have stopped speaking and are waiting for her to address you",
              "unique": true
            },
            {
              "name": "Vanguard-Captain Finrodin",
              "description": "the task of leading the vanguard to reclaim this tower.  He bends over the map as you enter, marks it with a charcoal stub, and barely looks up.",
              "unique": true
            }
          ]
        },
