          "vnum": 160,
          "name": "Vanguard's Respite",
          "description": "What was once a derelict room is now filled with makeshift cots and sparse furnishings. A simple counter of salvaged wood stands in one corner. Worn maps and strategic plans are pinned along the wall above it. Soldiers come here to sleep and to argue about where to go next.",
